Global Zinc Pyrithione Market Insights
Zinc Pyrithione Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Zinc Pyrithione Market Overview
The global Zinc Pyrithione market size was valued at USD 500 million in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 800 million by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% during the forecast period. Zinc Pyrithione is a key ingredient in personal care and cosmetic products due to its antifungal and antibacterial properties. It is widely used in shampoos, skincare products, and as a preservative in the pharmaceutical industry. The increasing prevalence of scalp conditions like dandruff, rising demand for anti-aging skincare products, and growth in the pharmaceutical sector are some of the factors driving the market's growth.

